S_n
\{1, \ldots, n\}
a=(a_1, \ldots, a_{2M})
n
M \gg n
f: S_n \longrightarrow R
c_k=\frac{{n\choose k}{2M-n \choose M-k}}{2M\choose M}
 f(\pi)=c_k\sum_{k=0}^n\left|\sum_{i=1}^ka_{\pi(i)}-\sum_{i=k+1}^{n}a_{\pi(i)}\right|, 
L
|f(\pi)-f(\sigma)|\leq L\, d(\pi, \sigma)
d(\pi, \sigma)=\#\{i: \pi(i) \neq\sigma(i), \pi, \sigma\in S_n\}
\pi, \sigma \in S_n
 |f(\pi)-f(\sigma)| \leq  c_k \sum_{k=0}^n\left|\sum_{i=1}^k (a_{\pi(i)}-a_{\sigma(i)}) - \sum_{i=k+1}^n (a_{\pi(i)}-a_{\sigma(i)})\right| 
